Looking for a place to watch movies, play, and hang out with friends? Hop onto Kast and start sharing experiences real-time!

points.quoteText: Company reserves the right to remove, delete, block, edit or modify any User Content or suspend or stop the Sharing of User Content at any time, without prior notice and at in its sole discretion for any reason or no reason.

points.title: The service can delete your account without prior notice and without a reason
points.quoteText: we also reserve the right to terminate, limit or suspend your access to or use of the Site and/or Company Services at any time and for any reason or no reason.
